data.meta_description: Team Concepts LLC | 40 followers on LinkedIn. Team Concepts started with the vision to positively change the world by empowering people to LIVE.  We design, craft, and innovate engaging team building activities and transformational training that activate people into pivotal moments, setting them on the path of success.   For the past 20 years we have been partnering with businesses, organizations, schools, and athletic teams from across the midwest empowering them to Be engaged.
